overview:
USB A Input 12-24V/2.4A
USB C Input 5V/3A, 9V/2A, 12V/1.5A
Output 5V/3A, 9V/2A, 12V/1.5A
Total Power 18W
Power Source Car Lighter Slot
Fast Charge Protocols QC 4.0 & PD 3.0
EAN/UPC 6957303837809

Fast charging your smartphone while you’re driving is a lot more useful than not charging it at all or using a standard port. That’s because you may be heavily using your phone at home, then you have to commute somewhere and you find that your battery is low. A fast charging car charger can charge a smartphone a lot faster by the time you reach your destination.
In this review, we’re taking a look at this UGREEN 18W Power Delivery and Quick Charge car charger. The car charger has everything you need for fast charging while you’re driving, but let’s take a closer look.
There are two ports on this car charger. One USB-C Power Delivery port and the other is a USB-A Quick Charge 3.0 port. The USB-C Power Delivery port is useful for basically fast charging most smartphones on the market as most modern smartphones are now Power Delivery compatible.

You’re also able to fast charge iPhones with the Power Delivery port, but remember that you’ll need a Lightning to USB-C cable for fast charging iPhones. The Power Delivery on UGREEN car charger has an 18W charging speed, enough for fast charging smartphones, but it’s not enough for charging most USB-C PD compatible laptops.

1.74" LARGE COLOR SCREEN
Xiaomi Band 8 Pro features a 1.74" AMOLED 2D colorful touch screen with 100% of P3 color gamut with a resolution of 336×480 pixels, 336 PPI, and up to 600 nits brightness, offering a stunning visual experience, engaging interface, and smart message notification.

FUNCTION
Xiaomi Band 8 Pro is equipped with a heart-rate monitor, SpO2 sensor, sleep tracker, and a menstrual cycle monitor for women. The wearable device is also capable of tracking stress levels and offering breath training.

GNSS CHIP
The Xiaomi Band 8 Pro has a built-in GNSS chip supporting five satellite systems.

150 SPORTS MODES
Xiaomi Band 8 Pro supports for more than 150 sports modes along with smart running mode and running lessons.

SMART HOME CONTROL
Xiaomi Band 8 Pro has the function of smart home control, turn the lights on and off in one sentence, and control home appliances such as Mijia air conditioners, sweeping robots, rice cookers, and purifiers.

5ATM WATER RESISTANCE
50 Meters Water Resistance withstands pressures equivalent to a depth of 50 meters, suitable for all-day wear, including swimming, showering, and hand washing.

POWERFUL BATTERY
Xiaomi Band 8 Pro packs a 297mAh battery that will last up to 14 days on a full charge. It is equipped with magnetic charging. It takes 2 hours to charge fully via a pogo pin charger.

ANDROID 6.0+ OR IOS 12.0+
Xiaomi Band 8 Pro can be paired with devices running Android 6.0+ or iOS 12.0+ via Bluetooth 5.1.

OTHER FEATURES
Xiaomi Band 8 Pro supports up to 100+ watch faces, take pictures remotely, play music, find phone, mute phone, unlock the phone, unlock notebook, call reminder, do not disturb phone, WeChat reminder, APP message reminder, calendar reminder, event reminder, weather forecast, timer, countdown, alarm clock, Bluetooth broadcast, online dial, custom dial, preset dial, screen lock, off-wrist detection, charging progress display, choice of wearing method, OTA upgrade.
